methods.description:
Opens a custom component within a modal.

Example :
this.modalService.open(ModalContentComponent, {
  modal: {
    enter: 'enter-scale-down 0.1s ease-out',
    leave: 'fade-out 0.5s',
  },
  overlay: {
    leave: 'fade-out 0.3s',
  },
  data: {
    type: 'Angular modal library',
  },
})
.subscribe((dataFromComponent) => {
   ...
});
